{"tid":1514290,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"全部中學生同我入晒黎！","createTime":"2019-08-28T16:28:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T16:30:33.000Z","uid":263310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"adca4c84ffbb6a912a933641fd6fea1f5b5185fa","tid":1514290,"uid":263310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:28:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">閱讀前注意：小弟只是深黃的中學生一名，文法文句不太好，如果有任何得罪勿屌多包涵多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港政府不但係兩個多月黎各界人士既訴求不秋不睬，完全視二百萬市民之意為身外之物，警犬既行為更加係令人髮指，不可接受。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所以作為中學生既我地唔可以再沉默當下，唔應該再怕去表達自己既立場，所以我地係時候都要係學校做翻啲嘢。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">係我地學校已經發起<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">口罩革命</span></span>，由2/9號開始每日返學戴口罩（最好係黑色，冇黑色都冇所謂），直到香港政府肯接納我地既訴求為止，請各位同學可以一同實行！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不割席，不篤灰</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不受傷，不被捕</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">保護自己，保護同伴</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">利申：以上內容全屬發夢</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">（唔識整海報，如有識整的希望可以幫手整同宣傳多謝）</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dZxUViF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdZxUViF.png&h=0e106155&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53d7517b4f9a8a79ee11c0c45865882ba6e8958f","tid":1514290,"uid":263310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"adca4c84ffbb6a912a933641fd6fea1f5b5185fa","tid":1514290,"uid":263310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,